  "reference_number": "RUS0693",
  "remarks": "\n Maxim Gennadyevich RESHETNIKOV, hereafter RESHETNIKOV, is Minister of Economic Development of the Russian Federation. He engaged in the promotion and implementation of a Russian government socio-economic plan for the development of Crimea and Sevastopol, areas illegally annexed by Russia in 2014. \n Consequently, RESHETNIKOV is or has been responsible for, engaged in, provided support for, or promoted policies and actions which have destabilised Ukraine and undermined or threatened the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine.   \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
